The Regulations requires insurance companies to put in place Board approved policy for 
protecting the interest of the Policyholders inter alia covering the following: 

a) Steps to be taken for enhancing Insurance Awareness; 
b) Service parameters including turnaround times for service rendered; 
c) Procedure for expeditious resolution of complaints; 
